What Am I Looking At?
This sheet is a repository which logs all present scores for switches that I've reviewed at length and via scorecards to date. The sheet is split into three tabs, with this comprising the full scoring while the 'Hard' and 'Soft' total tabs focus on only specific parts of the scoring. 
Above is a table of 'Manufacutrer Statistics' which groups and collects average scores of switches based on their manufacturer of origin. (Note: Switches with unknown manufacturers are not featured on this list)
As of 8/25/24, 'Time Weighted Total' scores were introduced and form the basis of the ranking system used to organize these switches. Scores decay at a rate of 1.0 points per year from the date in which they were last scored.
